Preheat a large saucepan.Heat the duck fat or olive oil in the saucepan.  Add the butter.Add the onions and sauté for 2 mins.Add the leek and carrot and sauté for 2 mins.Add the red wine and vegetable stock.  Bring soup to the boil and then simmer for 8-10 mins.Add the herb before removing soup from heat.Ladle the soup into bowls and serve.